name: Florence Broadhurst Stampede Therapeutic Eye Pillow
description:
Pamper yourself, relax, unwind...glamorously!

Heat your eye pillow in the microwave for 30 seconds (give or take a little) and place it over your eyes, inhale the lavender scent and relax. This versatile little pamper pillow can also be placed in the freezer (in a snap-lock bag) and used as a soothing eye pillow, this can especially help with eye puffiness. You can also use it as a an 'ouch' pillow, much more pleasing to the eye than the frozen peas!

These therapeutic pillows are great for:
Headaches
Sinus issues and allergies
Eye puffiness
Tired eyes
Relaxation
Neck/back/muscle aches and pains
Bumps and hurts

Approx 21cm x 9cm - filled with rice and lavender buds

Each pillow is made individually to order and the cut of fabric will vary with each pillow, making each one truly unique! 
IMPORTANT: Made to order - 7 days plus postage time.
